---
import InnerLayout from '../layouts/InnerLayout.astro';
---
<InnerLayout
  title="Lanka Ventures & LVL Energy Fund — HNB Investment Bank"
  description="Sri Lanka's dedicated listed venture capital vehicle — bridging growth capital with patient, long-term ownership. CSE listed: LVL.N0000."
  active="businesses"
>
  <style is:global>
    /* ── Lanka Ventures page-specific ── */
    .fo-a-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
    .fo-a-copy p { color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .fo-pillars { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.5rem; }
    .fo-pillar { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-left: 3px solid var(--accent); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.125rem 1.25rem; }
    .fo-pillar h4 { font-size: 0.925rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .fo-pillar p  { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--ink-2); margin: 0; line-height: 1.55; }
    .fo-stat-panel { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .fo-stat-panel h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .fo-stat { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0.625rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .fo-stat:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .fo-stat-label { font-size: 0.825rem; color: var(--ink-2); }
    .fo-stat-val   { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); }

    .fo-b-wrap { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px; gap: 3rem; align-items: start; }
    .fund-timeline { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }
    .ft-item { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 72px 1fr; gap: 0 1.5rem; }
    .ft-year { font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); padding-top: 0.25rem; text-align: right; }
    .ft-connector { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; }
    .ft-dot  { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--primary); flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.3rem; }
    .ft-line { width: 2px; flex: 1; background: var(--line); min-height: 40px; }
    .ft-body { padding-bottom: 1.75rem; }
    .ft-body h4 { font-size: 0.925rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .ft-body p  { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
    .cse-card { background: var(--primary); color: #fff; border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; }
    .cse-card .cse-label  { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; opacity: 0.7; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .cse-card .cse-ticker { font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    .cse-card .cse-price  { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .cse-card .cse-change { font-size: 0.875rem; opacity: 0.85; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
    .cse-card .cse-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .cse-meta-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 0.625rem; }
    .cse-meta-row .cse-meta-lbl { font-size: 0.78rem; opacity: 0.7; }
    .cse-meta-row .cse-meta-val { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; }
    .cse-note { font-size: 0.72rem; opacity: 0.55; margin-top: 1.25rem; }

    .fo-c-inner { background: var(--primary); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 3.5rem; color: #fff; }
    .fo-c-inner .section-label { color: oklch(0.65 0.165 140); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .fo-c-inner h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 2.25rem; }
    .fo-c-inner p  { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .fo-c-kpis { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); }
    .fo-c-kpi .kpi-val   { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; }
    .fo-c-kpi .kpi-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-top: 0.25rem; }
    .fo-c-ctas { display: flex; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
    .btn-primary-inv-lv { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: #fff; color: var(--primary); border: none; border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-ghost-inv-lv   { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem; background: transparent; color: #fff; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.45); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: none; }

    .port-grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .port-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; }
    .port-card-header { background: var(--bg-2); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
    .port-logo-placeholder { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--frame); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--muted); flex-shrink: 0; }
    .port-card-header h4 { font-size: 0.925rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.125rem; }
    .port-card-header .port-sector { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .port-card-body { padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem; }
    .port-card-body p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
    .port-meta { display: flex; gap: 0.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .port-tag  { font-size: 0.72rem; background: var(--bg-2); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: 4px; padding: 0.2rem 0.5rem; color: var(--ink-2); }

    .port-b-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 1fr; gap: 2rem; align-items: start; }
    .port-feat-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-top: 3px solid var(--primary); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 2rem; }
    .port-feat-card .pf-badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--primary); color: #fff; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .port-feat-card h3 { font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .port-feat-card p  { font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .port-feat-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin-top: 1.25rem; padding-top: 1.25rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .port-feat-stat .pfs-val   { font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); }
    .port-feat-stat .pfs-label { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.125rem; }
    .port-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.875rem; }
    .port-list-item { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1rem 1.25rem; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; }
    .pli-icon { width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; background: var(--bg-2); border: 1px solid var(--line); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .pli-icon svg { width: 18px; height: 18px; stroke: var(--primary); fill: none; stroke-width: 2; }
    .pli-info h4 { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.1rem; }
    .pli-info p  { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ink-2); margin: 0; }
    .pli-val { margin-left: auto; font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); white-space: nowrap; }

    .port-c-wrap { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; align-items: start; }
    .sector-map-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
    .sector-bars-v { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.875rem; }
    .sbv-row   { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 160px 1fr 60px; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: center; }
    .sbv-label { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--ink-2); }
    .sbv-track { height: 10px; background: var(--bg-2); border-radius: 5px; overflow: hidden; }
    .sbv-fill  { height: 100%; background: var(--primary); border-radius: 5px; }
    .sbv-val   { font-size: 0.82rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); text-align: right; }
    .nav-summary { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; }
    .nav-summary h4 { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); padding-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .nav-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding: 0.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
    .nav-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .nav-row-label { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-2); }
    .nav-row-val   { font-size: 0.925rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); }

    .ip-a-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; }
    .ip-card { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.75rem; }
    .ip-step-num { font-size: 2.25rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--line); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1; }
    .ip-card h4  { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .ip-card p   { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
    .ip-card ul  { padding-left: 1.1rem; }
    .ip-card ul li { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-2); margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }

    .ip-flow { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); gap: 0; position: relative; }
    .ip-flow::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 28px; left: 10%; right: 10%; height: 2px; background: var(--line); z-index: 0; }
    .ip-step { text-align: center; position: relative; z-index: 1; padding: 0 0.75rem; }
    .ip-step-circle { width: 56px; height: 56px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--bg); border: 2px solid var(--primary); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary); }
    .ip-step h4 { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.375rem; }
    .ip-step p  { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.5; }
    .ip-criteria { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; }
    .ip-criterion { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--line); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.25rem; }
    .ip-criterion h5 { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); margin-bottom: 0.375rem; }
    .ip-criterion p  { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-2); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }

    .ip-c-outer { background: var(--primary); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 3rem; color: #fff; }
    .ip-c-outer .section-label { color: oklch(0.65 0.165 140); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .ip-c-outer h2 { color: #fff; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .ip-c-outer > p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.7; }
    .ip-c-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; }
    .ip-c-tile { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1.5rem; }
    .ip-c-tile .tile-icon { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
    .ip-c-tile h4 { font-size: 0.925rem; font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 0.375rem; }
    .ip-c-tile p  { font-size: 0.8rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); line-height: 1.55; margin: 0; }
    .ip-c-bottom { margin-top: 2.5rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 2rem; }
    .ip-c-bottom p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); font-size: 0.875rem; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 480px; margin: 0; }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .fo-a-grid, .fo-b-wrap, .port-b-grid, .port-c-wrap { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .fo-c-kpis { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .port-grid-3, .ip-a-grid, .ip-criteria { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .ip-flow { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
      .ip-flow::before { display: none; }
      .ip-c-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .port-grid-3, .ip-a-grid, .ip-criteria, .ip-c-grid, .fo-c-kpis { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .ip-flow { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .ip-c-bottom { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>

  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header-inner">
      <span class="section-label">Our Businesses</span>
      <h1>Lanka Ventures &amp; LVL Energy Fund</h1>
      <p class="page-header-sub">Sri Lanka's dedicated listed venture capital vehicle — bridging growth capital with patient, long-term ownership.</p>
      <div class="page-header-meta">
        <span class="pill">CSE Listed: LVL.N0000</span>
        <span class="pill-accent">Venture Capital</span>
        <span class="pill">Regulated by SEC</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="page-body">

    <!-- S1 Fund Overview -->
    <section class="section-host" data-section-id="fund-overview" data-section-label="Fund Overview" data-default-variant="A">

      <div class="variant" data-variant="A">
        <div class="section-wrap scroll-fade">
          <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="fo-a-grid">
              <div class="fo-a-copy">
                <span class="section-label">Fund Overview</span>
                <h2>Growth Capital for Sri Lanka's Emerging Leaders</h2>
                <p>Lanka Ventures Limited (LVL) is Sri Lanka's only publicly listed venture capital company on the Colombo Stock Exchange (LVL.N0000). Established to channel patient capital into high-potential enterprises, LVL focuses on sectors driving Sri Lanka's economic transformation — energy, technology, and export-led businesses.</p>
                <p>Through LVL Energy Fund, we provide structured growth capital to companies that are past the early stage but need a committed partner with capital, governance expertise, and strategic network to achieve the next inflection point.</p>
                <div class="fo-pillars">
                  <div class="fo-pillar"><h4>Patient Capital Framework</h4><p>Holding periods of 5–10 years allow portfolio companies to grow without short-term exit pressure — rare in the Sri Lankan market.</p></div>
                  <div class="fo-pillar"><h4>Active Ownership</h4><p>Board representation, management advisory, and strategic introductions across the HNB Group network on every investment.</p></div>
                  <div class="fo-pillar"><h4>Listed Liquidity</h4><p>As a CSE-listed vehicle, investors in LVL gain exposure to a diversified portfolio of private growth companies with daily market liquidity.</p></div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="fo-stat-panel">
                <h3>Fund Snapshot</h3>
                <div class="fo-stat"><span class="fo-stat-label">CSE Ticker</span><span class="fo-stat-val">LVL.N0000</span></div>
                <div class="fo-stat"><span class="fo-stat-label">Last Traded Price</span><span class="fo-stat-val">LKR 17.40</span></div>
                <div class="fo-stat"><span class="fo-stat-label">Market Capitalisation</span><span class="fo-stat-val">LKR 1.74Bn</span></div>
                <div class="fo-stat"><span class="fo-stat-label">NAV per Share</span><span class="fo-stat-val">LKR 19.85</span></div>
                <div class="fo-stat"><span class="fo-stat-label">Portfolio Companies</span><span class="fo-stat-val">8 Active</span></div>
                <div class="fo-stat"><span class="fo-stat-label">Total AUM</span><span class="fo-stat-val">LKR 2.9Bn</span></div>
                <div class="fo-stat"><span class="fo-stat-label">Fund Inception</span><span class="fo-stat-val">2004</span></div>
                <div class="fo-stat"><span class="fo-stat-label">Fund Manager</span><span class="fo-stat-val">HNB Investment Bank</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="variant" data-variant="B">
        <div class="section-wrap scroll-fade">
          <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="section-header">
              <span class="section-label">Fund Overview</span>
              <h2>Two Decades of Growth Capital in Sri Lanka</h2>
              <p>From a seed-stage concept to Sri Lanka's only listed venture vehicle — the story of LVL traces the arc of private market development in Sri Lanka.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="fo-b-wrap">
              <div class="fund-timeline">
                <div class="ft-item"><div class="ft-year">2004</div><div class="ft-connector"><div class="ft-dot"></div><div class="ft-line"></div></div><div class="ft-body"><h4>Lanka Ventures Founded</h4><p>Established as a wholly-owned subsidiary of HNB to provide structured growth capital to Sri Lankan enterprises in underserved sectors.</p></div></div>
                <div class="ft-item"><div class="ft-year">2007</div><div class="ft-connector"><div class="ft-dot"></div><div class="ft-line"></div></div><div class="ft-body"><h4>CSE Listing</h4><p>LVL.N0000 listed on the Colombo Stock Exchange, becoming Sri Lanka's first and only publicly traded venture capital vehicle. IPO oversubscribed 3×.</p></div></div>
                <div class="ft-item"><div class="ft-year">2011</div><div class="ft-connector"><div class="ft-dot"></div><div class="ft-line"></div></div><div class="ft-body"><h4>LVL Energy Fund Launch</h4><p>Dedicated energy-sector vehicle formed in response to Sri Lanka's power generation shortfall — targeting renewables, grid infrastructure, and fuel distribution.</p></div></div>
                <div class="ft-item"><div class="ft-year">2016</div><div class="ft-connector"><div class="ft-dot"></div><div class="ft-line"></div></div><div class="ft-body"><h4>Portfolio Expansion</h4><p>AUM crossed LKR 1Bn. Portfolio extended beyond energy into technology services, agri-processing, and healthcare logistics.</p></div></div>
                <div class="ft-item"><div class="ft-year">2023</div><div class="ft-connector"><div class="ft-dot"></div><div class="ft-line"></div></div><div class="ft-body"><h4>Strategic Realignment</h4><p>Post-economic crisis, LVL recalibrated its mandate — focusing on export-revenue businesses and energy transition opportunities aligned with Sri Lanka's IMF program conditions.</p></div></div>
                <div class="ft-item"><div class="ft-year">2025</div><div class="ft-connector"><div class="ft-dot"></div></div><div class="ft-body"><h4>Today: LKR 2.9Bn AUM, 8 Active Positions</h4><p>Fully integrated into HNB Investment Bank's M&amp;A and capital markets origination pipeline.</p></div></div>
              </div>
              <div>
                <div class="cse-card">
                  <div class="cse-label">CSE Listed Security</div>
                  <div class="cse-ticker">LVL.N0000</div>
                  <div class="cse-price">LKR 17.40</div>
                  <div class="cse-change">▲ LKR 0.30 (+1.75%) today</div>
                  <hr class="cse-divider" />
                  <div class="cse-meta-row"><span class="cse-meta-lbl">52W High</span><span class="cse-meta-val">LKR 19.20</span></div>
                  <div class="cse-meta-row"><span class="cse-meta-lbl">52W Low</span><span class="cse-meta-val">LKR 12.80</span></div>
                  <div class="cse-meta-row"><span class="cse-meta-lbl">P/NAV</span><span class="cse-meta-val">0.88×</span></div>
                  <div class="cse-meta-row"><span class="cse-meta-lbl">Market Cap</span><span class="cse-meta-val">LKR 1.74Bn</span></div>
                  <div class="cse-meta-row"><span class="cse-meta-lbl">Shares Outstanding</span><span class="cse-meta-val">100,000,000</span></div>
                  <div class="cse-meta-row"><span class="cse-meta-lbl">Sector</span><span class="cse-meta-val">Investment Trusts</span></div>
                  <div class="cse-note">Prices delayed 20 minutes. Not investment advice.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="variant" data-variant="C">
        <div class="section-wrap scroll-fade">
          <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="fo-c-inner">
              <span class="section-label">Fund Overview</span>
              <h2>Sri Lanka's Only Listed Venture Capital Vehicle</h2>
              <p>LVL is built on a simple conviction: Sri Lanka's best growth companies deserve patient capital from an owner that understands the local operating environment as deeply as any global fund. We don't time exits around fund cycles — we stay for the cycle that creates real enterprise value.</p>
              <p>The LVL Energy Fund concentrates this mandate on Sri Lanka's energy transition: solar, wind, hydro, grid infrastructure, and the enabling services businesses that the energy transformation requires.</p>
              <div class="fo-c-kpis">
                <div class="fo-c-kpi"><div class="kpi-val">LKR 2.9Bn</div><div class="kpi-label">AUM</div></div>
                <div class="fo-c-kpi"><div class="kpi-val">8</div><div class="kpi-label">Portfolio Companies</div></div>
                <div class="fo-c-kpi"><div class="kpi-val">20+ yrs</div><div class="kpi-label">Track Record</div></div>
                <div class="fo-c-kpi"><div class="kpi-val">3×</div><div class="kpi-label">IPO Oversubscription</div></div>
              </div>
              <div class="fo-c-ctas">
                <a href="/investor-relations/" class="btn-primary-inv-lv">Investor Relations</a>
                <a href="#portfolio" class="btn-ghost-inv-lv">View Portfolio</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <!-- S2 Portfolio -->
    <section class="section-host" id="portfolio" data-section-id="portfolio" data-section-label="Portfolio">

      <div class="variant" data-variant="A">
        <div class="section-wrap scroll-fade" style="background:var(--bg-2);">
          <div class="section-inner">
            <div class="section-header">
              <span class="section-label">Portfolio</span>
              <h2>8 Active Portfolio Companies</h2>
              <p>Concentrated positions in businesses with defensible market positions, experienced management, and clear paths to scale.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="port-grid-3">
